00:08:54.664 --> 00:08:57.194
Oke?  - Ya.  Saya berjanji.

00:08:57.284 --> 00:08:59.146
Jangan khawatir.  Oke?

00:09:02.399 --> 00:09:04.245
Apa yang kalian berdua lakukan?

